    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "```\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<Configuration status=\"INFO\" monitorInterval=\"5\">\n  <Properties>\n    <Property name=\"root.log.level\">INFO</Property>\n  <Property name=\"basePath\">/var/log/besu</Property>\n  </Properties>\n\n  <Appenders>\n    <Console name=\"Console\" target=\"SYSTEM_OUT\">\n      <PatternLayout pattern=\"%d{yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSSZZZ} | %t | %-5level | %c{1} | %msg %throwable{short.message}%n\" />\n    </Console>\n\n        <RollingFile name=\"fileLogger\"\n                        fileName=\"${basePath}/besu.log\"\n                        filePattern=\"${basePath}/besu-%d{yyyy-MM-dd}.log\">\n                        <PatternLayout>\n                                <pattern>[%-5level] %d{yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%t] %c{1} - %msg%n\n                                </pattern>\n                        </PatternLayout>\n                        <Policies>\n                                <SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy size=\"10MB\" />\n                        </Policies>\n                        <!-- Max 10 files will be created everyday -->\n                        <DefaultRolloverStrategy max=\"100\">\n                        </DefaultRolloverStrategy>\n                </RollingFile>\n  </Appenders>\n  <Loggers>\n    <!-- Netty and DevP2P -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.netty\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.netty.NettyPeerConnection\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.netty.NettyP2PNetwork\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n\n    <!-- Peer Discovery -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.discovery\" level=\"DEBUG\"/>\n\n    <!-- Peer management -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.rlpx.RlpxAgent\" level = \"TRACE\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.p2p.rlpx\" level = \"DEBUG\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.manager\" level=\"DEBUG\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.manager.EthProtocolManager\" level=\"TRACE\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.manager.EthProtocolLogger\" level=\"DEBUG\"/>\n\n    <!-- Permissioning -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.permissioning\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n\n    <!-- Privacy -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.privacy\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.mainnet.precompiles.privacy\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <!-- Migration -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.privacy.storage.migration\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n\n    <!-- TX Mining and Processing -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.core.TransactionPool\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.mainnet.MainnetTransactionProcessor\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.blockcreation\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n\n    <!-- EVM -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.evm\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.evm.operation\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.evm.operation.RevertOperation\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n\n    <!-- Syncing -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.sync\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.eth.sync.BlockPropagationManager\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n\n    <!-- RPC APIs -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.api.jsonrpc\" level=\"INFO\"/>\n    <Logger name=\"org.hyperledger.besu.ethereum.api.jsonrpc.websocket\" level=\"WARN\"/>\n\n    <!-- DNS -->\n    <Logger name=\"org.apache.tuweni.discovery.DNSTimerTask\" level=\"WARN\"/>\n\n    <Root level=\"${sys:root.log.level}\">\n      <AppenderRef ref=\"Console\" />\n      <AppenderRef ref=\"fileLogger\"/>\n    </Root>\n  </Loggers>\n</Configuration>\n```",
